Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.90,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知为什么 也有种不可思议的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.93,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊? 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}早晨起来后你就一直在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  做了一个孩童时代的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:02:59.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.64,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}倒是你  还在继续做着那个梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨晚的那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和目前做过的梦截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.40,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天上挂着一轮月亮 皎洁耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而我  正在试图冲向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.81,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}向着高处边飞边感觉到身体阵阵作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.53,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后我听到了声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是很多人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.92,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们想把我封印起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的耳朵中嗡嗡轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就再也飞不高了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了  一会见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:38.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  小心别…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:42.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～姐姐你看  好棒耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明明没用绳子  是如何让它走起来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎呀  摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.32,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈哈  又站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小孩子就应该是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.65,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对了  你不去陪着佳乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦… 今天做饲养员的工作所以去了学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么嘛  我们怎么会在若无其事的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了  咱们得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小人偶  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘻嘻  握手握手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:31.55,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.11,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这就是所谓的情同手足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我又白干了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.36,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃这家伙真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:01.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}远野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是国崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想说话就先把东西咽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多谢  我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}粗茶淡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃没来过这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:19.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:20.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:24.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐呐  明天也给我做煎肉饼好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.41,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是贪吃的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:36.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放～手～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.90,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你先放！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小～满～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.43,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}淋浴可以使用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.36,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:11.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎么会有这里的钥匙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:16.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的父亲曾经是这里的站长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:20.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然现在已经辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.92,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}现在在做其他的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:28.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对了  这个表示刚才的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.72,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:38.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是小满昨天找到的瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个是  星之沙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:46.11,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像星星的小宝宝一样的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.55,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎～ 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.87,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～ 沙沙作响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}国崎先生也有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:56.38,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是给我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:03.55,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  这样就每人都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:11.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这星之沙是我从父亲那里得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那时我还很小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那岂不是非常的珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:18.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  给国崎先生和小满的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃同学  像是已经回去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:36.11,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看来是在学校停留到很晚才走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:42.45,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对了  国崎先生接下来准备做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}欢迎来到天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:52.21,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～ 已经可以看到星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其他的成员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.14,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有其他成员的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:59.58,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.47,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我就是部长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.03,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这叫少数精锐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是这样吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那家伙经常来这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:19.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  这是第一次带她来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:26.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个  邀请您来没有给您添麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:27.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:37.03,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直想三个人一起进行天体观测来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.32,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为那孩子像是很喜欢国崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.18,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子和我在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}总是说国崎先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:55.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那孩子是喜欢国崎先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.93,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是让人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看的出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:03.41,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为那孩子是我的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的一半？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我和小满一直就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一起生活过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:19.36,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啵～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}国崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:22.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:27.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直是在一个人旅行是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:31.25,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有过像这样感受到温暖的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:36.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感受到和其他人在一起时的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}感受到为了谁而活着的愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也  应该是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.58,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然已经是很久以前了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:52.07,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那小满就回去了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.76,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那小满就  冲啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:01.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思  让您特意送我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没什么的
