Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.90,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去学校了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到时候就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.31,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天明明不是去学校的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小满… 做错什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}借给我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:17:59.86,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没事  看着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:04.48,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要啦  间接接吻好脏的  喂～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}别要求那么高了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.18,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肥皂泡真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:29.12,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}透明的  像天空一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:33.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是不是出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去美风家看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去美风家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  她不来咱们去找她就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不想去她家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.00,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你们不是朋友么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没有去过她家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我自己去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为还得去接观铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢谢你送我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思  我这就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.14,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不来吃晚饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.48,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有个地方要去  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.58,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨天我们见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:24.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个天文部的新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}稍微有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.98,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能叫一下你的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:31.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:34.68,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我家并没有女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您是不是找错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  开什么玩笑  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.41,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不去干活  在这干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风的母亲一直得有心病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每次有机会我都会去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:58.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直把长女美风看作是未能出生的二女儿小满
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从很早以前就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:04.93,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但她的症状似乎突然间发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在她明白过来二女儿小满根本不在了后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.64,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风的存在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:17.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在她脑海中  两个女儿变得从一开始就是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本来应该有个妹妹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:35.09,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个叫小满的  我心爱的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是爸爸带大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以妈妈好像一直都很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.70,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}即将诞生的小满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:48.20,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本应该可以填补妈妈的那份寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.48,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果美风的一个愿望可以实现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.71,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风会许什么愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:58.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯… 想要一个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.57,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈失去了心灵的寄托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:06.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以选择了在梦中生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.60,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我… 便是那梦中的一块残片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:12.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但是昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:16.43,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听雾岛大夫说妈妈梦到了小满流产时的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:18.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}按照雾岛大夫的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:22.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈也因此接受了现实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:27.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今早  妈妈看着我对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:29.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「你是谁」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已经无法回到从前了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:37.58,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这就是我的梦的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我以小满的存在而活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}梦的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:50.53,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的翅膀已经忘记了如何飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.85,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为我一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:57.00,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只是重复着拍打翅膀的样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}无法飞翔的翅膀  还会有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:42.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:45.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起我来  也许你更适合旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:47.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跟我走吧  远野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:52.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然  这样下去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.17,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:57.32,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.69,0:24:00.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不再是梦  是真真正正的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:07.25,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一切的一切  都是我的罪孽造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:05.07,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海が見たいって　その子は言ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:08.14,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}だけど　つれてってあげられなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.07,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}やりたいことがたくさんあったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.27,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}でも何一つしてあげられなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:18.90,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夏はまだ　始まったばかりなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:39.38,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人さん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.30,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人さん　朝だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.07,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}あ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.39,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}よかったね　霧島さんが元気になって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:41.57,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.03,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}わたしもね　あの羽を見た時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.90,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}何だか　不思議な気持ちになって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.93,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.84,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}あ？ なんか言ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.66,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}ぼーとしてる　起きたときから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.05,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}まぁ　いや　ちょっと昔の夢を見てな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:02:59.94,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.59,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大したことじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.64,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}それより　お前の方はまだ続いてるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.06,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}うん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.05,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夕べの夢はね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.31,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}いままでと全然違ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.40,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}月が浮かんでて　凄く明るかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.87,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}わたし　空に昇ろうとしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.81,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}体中がずきずき痛んで　ずっと高くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.53,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}そうしたら　声が聞こえてきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.33,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}声？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.09,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}たくさんの人の声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.92,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}みんながわたしを閉じ込めようとしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.05,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}耳の中はワンワン鳴って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.74,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}それ以上昇れなくなって…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.95,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}じゃ　また後でな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:38.68,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}うん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.89,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}行って来るね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:42.33,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}おい　気をつけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:42.78,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}わ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.01,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}わ～　凄いね　お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.09,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}糸も使ってないのに　どうやって歩いてるんだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.80,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}あれ？ 転けちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.32,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}はは 立った立った～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.17,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}やっぱり子ともはこうでなくちゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.65,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}しかしお前　佳乃のそばにいてやらなくていいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.94,jap for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}お… 今日は飼育員で学校に行ってるのか
